description:
Beary Tales - An Unusual Nature Fairytale | Wildlife Documentary

Watch 'Three Bear Cubs - Growing Up in a Dangerous World' here: https://youtu.be/mXqUtU8RDg0

Two orphaned bear cubs would’ve been destined to starvation – if a man had not adopted them. The touching documentary shows the bear twins’ childhood as they live with their new "mother". From the cubs' first steps, it follows their development from defenseless babies to cheeky teenagers.

Enjoy stories about nature, wildlife, culture, people, history and more to come.
